To install the node installer script 'toastinstall' please run this script from physical node:

sudo curl -sSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SirJBiscuit/toast-installer/main/nodeinstaller.sh | sed 's/\r$//' | sudo tee /usr/local/bin/toastinstall > /dev/null

sudo chmod +x /usr/local/bin/toastinstall



This script will allow you to make multiple nodes, much easier and faster.
Run script -> Follow Prompts -> Profit!
